1. *Mestima* treba da očistite pod. (You need to clean the floor in *places*.)
2. U ovom selu ima mnogo *mesta* koja vredi posetiti. (There are many *places* worth visiting in this village.)
3. Oni su *mestima* uspeli da ostvare svoje snove. (They managed to achieve their dreams in *some places*.)
4. *Mestima* je teško naći dobar restoran u ovom gradu. (It's difficult to find a good restaurant in this city *in some places*.)
5. Povrede na telu su najbolje lečiti hladnim *mestima*. (Body injuries are best treated with cold *places*.)
6. *Mestima* gde je gužva treba biti oprezan i strpljiv. (In *crowded places*, one should be careful and patient.)
7. Ovaj projekat će biti izveden na tri *mesta*. (This project will be carried out in three *places*.)
8. *Mestima* je bilo tako tiho da se čulo zvono u daljini. (It was so quiet in *some places* that the bell in the distance could be heard.)